Classes in synthlab.internal.modules that implement Module
 class ModuleEnvelope
          Concrete module class of ADSR Parameters are pass by UI, A,D,R in MilleSconde, S in percentage Parameters Gate is for manually, ExtermGate for a external control signal
 class ModuleKeyboard
          Concrete module class of keyboard 1 parameter octave control in volt manually support maximum 3 Touch in the same time 1 output signal
 class ModuleLFO
          Concrete module class of LFO 1 input for configuration his output signal frequency 1 output product low frequency sinusoidal wave signal
 class ModuleMixer
          Concrete module class of Mixer 4 signals input 4 gain parameters for each input, we can change them manually with UI 1 signal output which the son is mixed.
 class ModuleMultiplexer
          Concrete module class of Hub 1 input signal 4 output signal just transport the value of input
 class ModuleOut
          Concrete module class of Speaker who transport the signal to the son card 1 input signal only
 class ModuleOutToFile
          Concrete module class of RecordToFile 1 input signal waiting for the recording Parameters recording is for manually, control if writing or not to a son file
 class ModuleSequencer
          Concrete module class of Sequencer Product a song!
 class ModuleVCA
          Concrete module class of VCA 2 parameters , 1 for input signal, 1 for gain of this signal We can control the parameters gain(volume) manually in UI,or we can do it with a external control signal
 class ModuleVCF
          Concrete module class of VCF Parameters are cutOff in Hz, manually or externally; resonance in Db, manually add for the output signal 4 output signals, high pass, low pass, banned pass, Notch.
 class ModuleVCO
          Concrete module class of VCO 4 input signal control manually in UI or externally by connecting signal ,Active for switch this module ON/OFF, Constant for K, Frequency for fm Shape for change different wave form 1 output signal
